v1.headline: Daily post to fight your FOMO on AI.
v1.about:
I find the latest AI news and share it daily.

I work with Ruben Hassid, digging into the latest AI updates and testing new tools.

A lot of people are still skeptical about AI.
They either fear it, ignore it, or think it’s just hype.

But AI isn’t the future, it’s already here. 
And those who learn how to use it today will have the edge tomorrow.

I’m not ashamed of using AI to be more efficient. No one should be.
It’s not about replacing your skills, it’s about amplifying them.

To master AI with words (no code) → how-to-prompt.ai
